                        <div class="Message">
                            <a title="Link: https://lgcommunity.us.com/profile/aikiwolf" href="https://lgcommunity.us.com/profile/aikiwolf" rel="nofollow">aikiwolf</a>, this would not be possible in the TV. The updating of the folders would need to be performed on the PC. If the refresh rate of the folders can be set automatically, it would be in the Smart Share settings on the PC.                        </div>
